[LOOP CONTINUES]

21:34.684 --> 21:36.686
They got away?

21:36.730 --> 21:39.385
Not for long.

21:39.428 --> 21:43.824
HARUMI:
It's time to take
the trash out.

21:47.610 --> 21:49.525
